memberdef.name: MD_CmdHandlerTbl

briefdescription.para: Entry Point and main loop for the Memory Dwell task.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Call MD_AppInit to initialize the task. LOOP: Copy any newly loaded tables Pend on the Software Bus waiting to receive next message. If MD_WAKEUP_MID Message is received, call MD_DwellLoop to send whatever memory values are being 'dwelled on'. If MD_CMD_MID Message is received, call MD_ExecRequest for processing. If MD_SEND_HK_MID Message is received, call MD_HkStatus for processing.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: Associated with each dwell address is a 'Delay' which is the number of wake-up calls to wait before recording the next value for this Dwell Table. The 'Rate' value associated with Dwell Table is the sum of all individual delays. For a table to be dwelled on, its rate must be >=1.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Initialize all data elements. If this is a PROCESSOR_RESET, and saving dwell tables to CDS is indicated, then restore image from CDS.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: None
Any of the return values from CFE_ES_RegisterApp
Any of the return values from CFE_EVS_Register
Any of the return values from CFE_SB_CreatePipe
Any of the return values from CFE_SB_Subscribe
Any of the return values from CFE_TBL_Register
Any of the return values from CFE_TBL_Load

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Initialize control structures for each of the MD_NUM_DWELL_TABLES dwell streams.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: None
None

briefdescription.para: Initialize Software Bus Services for the Memory Dwell Task.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Create message pipe. Subscribe to all input and output messages.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: None
Any of the return values from CFE_SB_CreatePipe
Any of the return values from CFE_SB_Subscribe

briefdescription.para: Initialize Table Services for the Memory Dwell Task.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Register Tables with Table Services. Check for Recovered Tables. IF Recovered Tables Found THEN Retrieve them. Validate them. IF Recovered Tables are Invalid Initialize Tables ENDIF ELSE Initialize Tables.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: None
Any of the return values from CFE_TBL_Register
Any of the return values from CFE_TBL_Load

briefdescription.para: Check Table Status and take appropriate actions.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Checks status of Tables, and takes action if validation requests or update requests are pending.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: Assumes that an update is pending for the specified table.

parameterdescription.para: Dwell table identifier. Internal values [0..MD_NUM_DWELL_TABLES-1] are used.

entry.para: May return any value from CFE_TBL_GetStatus, CFE_TBL_Validate, or CFE_TBL_Update.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Processes messages obtained from the command pipe.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: None

parameterdescription.para: a pointer to the message received from the command pipe

briefdescription.para: Send Housekeeping Status to Health & Safety task.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: For each dwell table the housekeeping data includes: number of dwell addresses, number of counts for packet formation, data size in bytes, current entry in data processing, current offset in packet data field, countdown to next data collection.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: None

briefdescription.para: Compares message with MD_CmdHandlerTbl to identify the message.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Searches the Command Handler Table for an entry matching the message ID and, if necessary, the Command Code. If an entry is not located, an error code is returned.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: None

parameterdescription.para: message ID of command message received on command pipe
command code from command message received on command pipe

entry.para: On success, a non-negative Table Index is returned.
